<br>
This board was started, supported, and maintained by the enthusiasm, and the monetary contributions of serious board users who have made it quite clear in the past they want a degree of reason and maturity around here.  Yes, even in the Soapbox, and we've never pretended this isn't a moderated forum.  If you want a board where people say and do any damn thing they want, it is *very* easy to make one.<br>
<br>
Thing is, it isn't very fun ranting and frothing and cursing like a drunken sailor on a ffa board where everyone is doing the same thing.  Everyone wants to be the first and the only one pissing in the swimming pool, and everyone wants to bring their bile to an otherwise civil community. Now that, I won't have, and that's what moderation is all about.  I repeat.  Go ahead and make your own board if you want to.  No one is stopping you.<br>
<br>
Valquiss <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uermok.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ermok</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 13<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/14/02 5:05:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=369.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Moderators</span><hr size=1> The question is not about the board.  The title was moderators.  Basically what I mean to say it was... lighten up.  Some of us have better senses of humor.  Yes, some threads get immature to most standards, but watching people really go at each other is half the fun of EQ.  <br>
<br>
I love watching flame wars and dont want to have to go all over the net to find them.  The whole reason to rant is so that you will be heard by your peers.  I dont have anything to rant about, but I am sure lots of FVers do.  <br>
<br>
Ranting and raving is bitching.  You try to make a distinction but there simply isnt one.  A rant is an incoherant stream of nonsensical consciousness with as much offensive material as can be squeezed in.  Dennis Miller does not discuss, debate, or reflect, he has his own HBO show for his tyrades.  Dont tell me there is not an audience for rants.<br>
<br>
If you dont want to see it, and if others dont want to see it, dont read it.  If you do chose to read it, lighten up and take it for whatever its worth (no matter how pointless).  I can relate to you though, I too, sometimes enjoy the power trip of locking threads and blocking people's opinions.  Censorship is the ultimate high when you are in control. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=aradil>Aradil</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 86<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/14/02 5:15:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=369.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Moderators</span><hr size=1> What I do, when I'm in the mood to read really good rants, is go to Graffe's (<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.graffe.com">www.graffe.com</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->). Wizards swear like it's going out of style. If you're really feeling adventurous, you can check out the rant board of your favorite blue server. But this board is the board I go to when I want reasoned discussion about something or other. <br>
<br>
This isn't the only board in the world, is what I'm trying to say.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/usnoutfv.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Snout FV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 23<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/14/02 5:21:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=369.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Moderators</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>  pub6.ezboard.com/bnamelesstavern <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
